WEBVTT

1
00:21:03.561 --> 00:21:05.028 
我不想顾虑太多
I'm tired of overthinking things.

2
00:21:05.063 --> 00:21:07.231 
我要行动 6-0缝线
I need to take action! 6-0 prolene!

3
00:21:07.265 --> 00:21:10.400 
你要在公共场合见面
What you need to do is set up a date in a public place.

4
00:21:10.435 --> 00:21:12.302 
确保朋友知道你的行踪
Make sure your friends know where you're going.

5
00:21:12.337 --> 00:21:14.705 
永远要有退场策略
And always have an exit strategy.

6
00:21:14.739 --> 00:21:16.373 
告诉David M. 我今晚见他
Tell David M. I will meet him tonight

7
00:21:16.407 --> 00:21:18.142 
晚上八点 在大厅见
at 8:00 p.m. in the lobby.

8
00:21:18.497 --> 00:21:20.744 
- 好敢啊 - 太敢了吗
- Ooh, bold. - Too bold?

9
00:21:20.779 --> 00:21:24.715 
没有藏枪胆大 但也很厉害了
Not gun-in-the-oven bold,but bold nonetheless.

10
00:21:28.019 --> 00:21:32.089 
她真走运 子弹没伤到肠道或者主要器官
She's lucky the bullet didn't injure her bowel or any major vessels.

11
00:21:32.123 --> 00:21:35.225 
要有多蠢 才会为男人干这种事
How dumb do you have to be to do something like that for a guy?

